
<%= render partial: 'chooser' %>

<div id="setup-page">

  <div id="prepare-a-new-practice">
    <%= render partial: 'shared/home_page_logo' %>
    create&nbsp;your&nbsp;practice&nbsp;session
  </div>

  <table>
    <tr class="valign-top">
      <td id="languages-container">
        <div id="choose-language">language</div>
        <%= render partial: 'list_languages' %>
      </td>
      <td id="tests-container">
        <div id="choose-tests">tests</div>
        <%= render partial: 'list_tests' %>
      </td>
      <td>
        <div id="info-container">
            The starting files for your chosen language+tests are always the same;
            a function called <code>answer</code> that returns <code>6 * 9</code>
            and a test function called
            <code>life, the universe, and everything</code> that expects
            <code><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Hitchhiker%27s_Guide_to_the_Galaxy">42</a></code>
            <br/>
            <br/>
            The starting files are completely <em>unrelated</em> to your
            chosen exercise. They are simply an example to start you off.
            <br/>
            <br/>
            Tests must complete in 15 seconds.
            <br/>
            <br/>
            Beware copy-pasting code into the editor (eg from a blog article).
            This often inserts invisible characters into your code!
        </div>
        <br/>
        <%= render partial: 'next_button' %>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>


</div>


